The paper discusses a software framework for enabling real-time artificial intelligence on mainstream end devices without special hardware. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AR (Augmented Reality), and cs.SY (Systems and Control). However, given the focus on machine learning and deep neural networks, as well as the mention of DNN pruning and acceleration, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories. The other sub-categories are less likely but still possible given the potential applications of the CoCoPIE framework in computer vision, augmented reality, and control systems.
